## Objective weight hierarchy (at time of run)

compliance (legal=10, policy=5) >> quality (coverage=3, team_continuity=2) > balance/cost/efficiency (1–1.5).
This explains the 27% coverage + 672h workload variance: solver tolerates coverage shortfall rather than risk legal violations.

